===Etymology===
{{bor|en|fr|madeleine}}, from earlier {{m|fr|gâteau à la Madeleine}}, after the given name {{m|fr|Madeleine||Magdalene}}, of uncertain reference: attributed in some sources to a 19th-century pastry cook {{w|Madeleine Paulmier|lang=fr}}, whose existence is now considered dubious.<br/>In sense 2, used with reference to the cake's function in the extract below, taken from {{w|Marcel Proust}}'s ''{{w|In Search of Lost Time}}''.

